						"title": "Secure, fast, any-to-any connectivity between networks, apps, and users",
						"subtitle": "Connect, protect, and build your digital business with a connectivity cloud",
						"copy": "Organizations are investing in a wide variety of projects to upgrade their digital customer experience, empower their workforce with new digital tools, and better secure their network and broader digital environment. \n\nSo, why are 70% of new digital projects late, over-budget, or delivered out of scope?* Because many IT environments have become overly complex due to:\n- Decentralized security and networking functions across many cloud-based point services\n- Regional expansion\n- AI adoption\n\nThe solution: Consolidating IT and security on a new type of agile cloud platform: a connectivity cloud.\n\nExplore the ebook and learn how a connectivity cloud works, what it does, and how it drives stronger digital ROI. \n\n![Connectivity Cloud eBook - Thumbnail](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/1fJBDYKJf1tOdUCik0mjLN/f02bbce7b0d781f09dbfa89fc7aa373e/reduce-the-it-complexity-thats-holding-back-your-digital-projects-image.png)\n",
